---
// Hero Section
---

<section id="hero" class="hero">
  <div class="section-layout">
    <div class="section-sidebar" aria-hidden="true">
      <p class="hero-scroll-cue fade-in-up">* Research</br>* Product</br>* Taste</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="hero-intro fade-in-up">
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          把前沿 AI 的能力，做成用户真正愿意长期使用的产品。
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-lead">
          我关注模型能力与产品体验之间的转换过程：从算法边界、系统落地到交互表达。这里记录我正在构建的项目、持续研究的问题，以及对“好产品”判断标准的演化。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-grid fade-in-up">
        <div class="text-col" data-tone="now">
          <h3>Current Focus</h3>
          <div class="prose">
            <p>生成模型与 Agent 系统在真实场景下的可用性与可持续迭代。</p>
            <p>把研究结论转成可以验证、可以复用、可以被用户感知的产品能力。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-col" data-tone="next">
          <h3>What You Will See</h3>
          <div class="prose">
            <p>精选项目拆解：问题定义、关键取舍、以及最终带来的用户价值。</p>
            <p>阶段性思考与实验记录：关注趋势，更关注可落地的方法。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    isolation: isolate;
    overflow: clip;
    min-height: 100svh;
    padding-block: 0;
  }

  @supports not (height: 100svh) {
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 50%;
    width: 100vw;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: -2;
    background:
      radial-gradient(
        85% 74% at 14% 18%,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--content-tone-work-research) 20%, transparent),
        transparent 68%
      ),
      radial-gradient(
        66% 56% at 82% 74%,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--content-tone-signals-mind) 16%, transparent),
        transparent 70%
      ),
      linear-gradient(
        180deg,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg) 88%, white) 0%,
        color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg) 96%, transparent) 48%,
        var(--color-bg) 100%
      );
  }

  .hero::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    left: 50%;
    width: 100vw;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: -1;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.28;
    background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(
      0deg,
      transparent 0,
      transparent 3px,
      color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-text-muted) 4%, transparent) 4px
    );
  }

  .section-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 100%;
    align-content: end;
    padding-top: calc(var(--header-height) + var(--space-lg));
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .section-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    align-content: end;
  }

  .hero-intro {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    max-width: min(72ch, 100%);
  }

  .hero-kicker {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-ui);
    width: max-content;
    padding: 0.26rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-border) 80%, transparent);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg) 72%, transparent);
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5.4vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 1.04;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    max-width: 13.5ch;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .hero-lead {
    max-width: 56ch;
    font-size: clamp(1.04rem, 1.16vw, 1.24rem);
    color: color-mix(
      in srgb,
      var(--content-tone-default) 18%,
      var(--color-text)
    );
  }

  .text-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    padding-top: var(--space-md);
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-border) 82%, transparent);
  }

  .text-col h3 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--tone-strong, var(--color-text-muted));
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--tone-border, var(--color-border));
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.2vw, 1.25rem);
    color: color-mix(
      in srgb,
      var(--tone-solid, var(--content-tone-default)) 16%,
      var(--color-text)
    );
  }

  .hero-scroll-cue {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-text-muted) 82%, transparent);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .section-layout {
      grid-template-columns: var(--layout-sidebar-columns);
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-layout {
      padding-top: calc(var(--header-height) + var(--space-md));
      padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .text-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }
  }
</style>
